  "description": "There\u0026rsquo;s a weird cycle that isn\u0026rsquo;t really obvious yet with this current iteration of my research notes, but they\u0026rsquo;re working to be an implemented form of the same ideas. philosophy -\u0026gt; math -\u0026gt; tech -\u0026gt; content -\u0026gt; questions -\u0026gt; research -\u0026gt; philosophy. Philosophy and Questions are really the only parts that aren\u0026rsquo;t some form of encoding, and so are the only parts that really require generative creativity, so that\u0026rsquo;s what I\u0026quot;m trying to focus on.\n",
